# CODEOWNERS — out-of-tree trust anchor for the honesty gate.
#
# The gate guards artifacts but cannot guard itself from its own PR. Requiring
# code-owner review on the verifier files closes the gate-self-modify bypass:
# a PR that weakens/deletes the verifier needs steward approval to merge.
#
# Enforcement requires GitHub-side config (cannot be set in-tree):
#   Settings -> Branches -> protect `main` -> "Require review from Code Owners"
#   + mark `honesty-gate` a required status check. See REPAIR_AUDIT.json.

